data.description: Perfectly nestled in a convenient location in D66! Features include 2 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, partially finished basement, whirlpool tub, and shaded south-facing patio. 3-season porch off the main floor primary suite and living room. Beautiful hardwood floors on main floor entry, kitchen, living room and informal dining. Monthly HOA dues cover routine seasonal items of lawn care and snow removal. Just minutes from daily conveniences. Home sold as-is but is in good condition. See the potential of this home firsthand!
